{"id": "1311180991355686992", "channel_id": "1311180991355686992", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168738854837166162", "author_name": "lubi_17667", "author_bot": false, "content": "感謝各位守密人的支持！\n《忘卻前夜》OST：恐怖蠟像之館，今日發佈囉～歡迎大家收聽、下載及分享～如果有基於OST的二次創作，也歡迎分享給我們！（二創請遵照同人規則，OST內容請勿商用）\n\n忘卻前夜OST：恐怖蠟像之館\n蠟像館的規則有三條，第一，不可觸碰蠟像；第二，不可揭開蠟像的蓋布；第三，不可將血滴到蠟像館裏。千萬，千萬不要違反它們哦。\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n企劃：B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2024-11-27T04:05:08.904000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🥹", "emoji_id": null, "count": 18}, {"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 12}, {"emoji": "wish", "emoji_id": "1236951537788649492", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1311180992802979840", "filename": "-.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 4820406, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1311180991355686992/1311180992802979840/-.png?ex=69cc9975&is=69cb47f5&hm=11fe875445fca68f31501ace683951334f53669dcc1bf4e20628fdf00037a1a0&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1311180991355686992", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：恐怖蠟像之館", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1311181442117537893", "channel_id": "1311180991355686992", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168738854837166162", "author_name": "lubi_17667", "author_bot": false, "content": "1.甜蜜遊戲-Sweet Game-\n燭火嗶啵，皮鞭劈啪，歡迎加入潘狄婭的派對，請跟上遊戲的鼓點，迎接甜蜜的獎勵。", "timestamp": "2024-11-27T04:06:56.374000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1311181441861681172", "filename": "-Sweet_Game-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 18013592, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1311180991355686992/1311181441861681172/-Sweet_Game-.wav?ex=69cc99e0&is=69cb4860&hm=c256de5fcd2dfb3e01340109a0713a14e768799a32da379251857df95b274c67&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1311180991355686992", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：恐怖蠟像之館", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1311181641640841288", "channel_id": "1311180991355686992", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168738854837166162", "author_name": "lubi_17667", "author_bot": false, "content": "2.蠟像館之夜-Night at the Wax Museum-\n它們皮膚細膩，它們眼珠靈活，它們笑容燦爛。歡迎，歡迎新朋友。", "timestamp": "2024-11-27T04:07:43.944000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1311181641531785307", "filename": "-Night_at_the_Wax_Museum-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 19625042, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1311180991355686992/1311181641531785307/-Night_at_the_Wax_Museum-.wav?ex=69cc9a0f&is=69cb488f&hm=b773e7564e77185bffeaca614b98511e56e56e57398648e8a68c015924b0f14b&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1311180991355686992", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：恐怖蠟像之館", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1311181813934325761", "channel_id": "1311180991355686992", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168738854837166162", "author_name": "lubi_17667", "author_bot": false, "content": "3.凝固的面容-Frozen Face-\n蠟像偶爾的移位屬於館內正常現象，如果聽到腳步聲，請及時回頭；如果感到有人已貼在你的背後，請千萬別回頭。", "timestamp": "2024-11-27T04:08:25.022000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1311181813586071592", "filename": "-Frozen_Face-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 20357240, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1311180991355686992/1311181813586071592/-Frozen_Face-.wav?ex=69cc9a38&is=69cb48b8&hm=80e610566290cc9499ec458078f7d11cdc1290f011f1e99d9da190c2556aed51&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1311180991355686992", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：恐怖蠟像之館", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1311182047540412467", "channel_id": "1311180991355686992", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168738854837166162", "author_name": "lubi_17667", "author_bot": false, "content": "4.情景扮演-Scenario Play-\n他們曾是傭人、平民，甚至貴族。過去他們素不相識，現在他們手挽著手，共同扮演幸福的喜劇。", "timestamp": "2024-11-27T04:09:20.718000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1311182047074586726", "filename": "-Scenario_Play-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 40839482, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1311180991355686992/1311182047074586726/-Scenario_Play-.wav?ex=69cc9a70&is=69cb48f0&hm=1e83f59636a013fa0b4d2432a9a0dacb00bf2af9a775048319ee2307ab5a443b&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1311180991355686992", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：恐怖蠟像之館", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1311182128993533982", "channel_id": "1311180991355686992", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168738854837166162", "author_name": "lubi_17667", "author_bot": false, "content": "5. 24小姐-Miss 24-\n從蠟像中爬出一位美麗的小姐、一位恐懼的小姐、一位怯懦的小姐、一位瘋狂的小姐。別誤會，她們都是同一位小姐。", "timestamp": "2024-11-27T04:09:40.138000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1311182128419045436", "filename": "24-Miss_24-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 14325338, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1311180991355686992/1311182128419045436/24-Miss_24-.wav?ex=69cc9a84&is=69cb4904&hm=ea6cf475eff494573619d5d5709fc71eb6b61e7ebfaf9980221723c0284a0d46&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1311180991355686992", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：恐怖蠟像之館", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1311182379947266098", "channel_id": "1311180991355686992", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168738854837166162", "author_name": "lubi_17667", "author_bot": false, "content": "6.塑像師-Sculptor-\n別動呀，讓我給你畫上最美的笑容。", "timestamp": "2024-11-27T04:10:39.970000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1311182379586551920", "filename": "-Sculptor-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 15601294, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1311180991355686992/1311182379586551920/-Sculptor-.wav?ex=69cc9abf&is=69cb493f&hm=28f8897f9d8f96117a53a30b055f485afefd0b4b9ea8081c956dc472b83a3c04&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1311180991355686992", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：恐怖蠟像之館", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
